# Pick ONE setup and copy matching values into .env:
#
# A) docker compose up -d  (see docker-compose.yml, port 5432)
# B) Postgres.app          https://postgresapp.com  (port 5432)
# C) Supabase local CLI    supabase start           (port 54322)
# D) Supabase cloud        Project Settings → Database → connection string
